*SimpleTexting is hiring a Copywriter* :rocket:

*This is a full-time role.*

*What's the deal?* 

SimpleTexting is an online platform that makes it easy for businesses to text their customers. Our company is profitable, growing, and 100% remote. We're searching for a writer to join our small but mighty marking team. You’ll be asked to wordsmith blog posts, landing pages, help center articles, and more. 

The ideal candidate has at least two years of experience writing for another B2B SaaS company. A portfolio with long and short-form content is a must.

P.S. We offer excellent healthcare coverage for U.S. folks plus flexible PTO with a 10-day minimum!


*Learn more and apply here:* <https://simpletexting.com/job/copywriter/>

<@U01SKGL00JE>

*Obviously AI is hiring a Content Marketing Manager* :rocket:

*This is a full-time role.*

*What's the deal?* 

Obviously AI is a no-code AI based in San Francisco and we’re looking for a Content Marketing Manager to tell the world our story. 

Our no-code AI is built on the belief that giving non-technical business users access to machine learning so they can rapidly run predictions on their historical data — with just a few clicks — will be revolutionary. 

If this excites you, then we can't wait to learn more about you!

*Learn more and apply here:* <https://bit.ly/3fvYeoX>
